Royal Mix is a unified digital ecosystem combining Food Delivery, Health Services, Supplier Networks, Publicity Systems, and Smart City operations inside one secure, scalable application.

Modules include: Royal Food, Royal Health, Royal Delivery, Supplier Network, Publicity System (30-day rule), Rewards, Maps, Business Accounts, AI Engine, and Admin System.

Built for Zambia first (Lusaka launch), with national compliance (trading licenses, supplier verification, delivery transport rules, public health guidelines).

Technology: React Native / Flutter, Supabase PostgreSQL, RLS Security, OpenAI AI Engine, Fast API layer.

Suppliers: Coca-Cola, Pepsi, Milk/Fruit Networks, Local Markets, Royal Internal Production â€” all verified and announced through a mandatory 30-day publicity system.

Testnet Phase: Architecture, API routes, supplier logic, rewards system, security templates, Zambia compliance preparation.

Royal Mix is engineered to scale city-by-city, then nationwide, then globally.
